--
-- Categories (5 each):
--   A. AI dev tooling: Magic.dev, Windsurf, Greptile, Qodo, Ellipsis
--   B. AI design: Khroma, Relume, Magician, Galileo AI, Subframe
--   C. AI video / audio: Hailuo, Vidu, Hedra, Argil, Mureka
